LigrettoStop is an application, which supports you with counting points in Ligretto by Schmidt.

Firstly, choose how many players you have.
Secondly, write down each person to this app. People should have be written under unique names.
Then, set number of rounds (or draw it). If you draw it, you won't know how many rounds you will have.
Now, you can start playing.
If you want, you can print results during your game.
On the end of your game, this program will print your results.
Have a good time!
